      "text": "<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">A pregnant patient tests positive for Chlamydia trachomatis. What is the drug of choice for treating Chlamydia infection during pregnancy?</span></span></p>",
