          "text": "<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Distilled water or normal saline is the recommended diluent for the BCG vaccine.</span></span></span></span></p>"
        },
        {
          "id": 150628,
          "text": "<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">The injection site should be thoroughly cleaned with an antiseptic solution prior to vaccination.</span></span></span></span></p>"
