      "text": "<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">A 3-month-old female child who was recently vaccinated with the Bacillus Calmette-Gu&eacute;rin (BCG) vaccine comes for a follow-up. Which of the following statements about the BCG vaccination is correct?</span></span></p>",
